## Bugs Fixed During Testing 🐛

### PSR-4 Autoloading Violations (Critical)
Split 4 multi-class files (which caused `Cannot redeclare class` errors) into 12 proper PSR-4 files:

| Old File | New Files |
|----------|-----------|
| [AdminUserPages.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/barulagi/app/Filament/Resources/AdminUserResource/Pages/AdminUserPages.php) | [ListAdminUsers.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/barulagi/app/Filament/Resources/AdminUserResource/Pages/ListAdminUsers.php), [CreateAdminUser.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/barulagi/app/Filament/Resources/AdminUserResource/Pages/CreateAdminUser.php), [EditAdminUser.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/barulagi/app/Filament/Resources/AdminUserResource/Pages/EditAdminUser.php) |
| [ArticlePages.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/barulagi/app/Filament/Resources/ArticleResource/Pages/ArticlePages.php) | [ListArticles.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/barulagi/app/Filament/Resources/ArticleResource/Pages/ListArticles.php), [CreateArticle.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/barulagi/app/Filament/Resources/ArticleResource/Pages/CreateArticle.php), [EditArticle.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/barulagi/app/Filament/Resources/ArticleResource/Pages/EditArticle.php) |
| [DiscountPages.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/barulagi/app/Filament/Resources/DiscountResource/Pages/DiscountPages.php) | [ListDiscounts.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/barulagi/app/Filament/Resources/DiscountResource/Pages/ListDiscounts.php), [CreateDiscount.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/barulagi/app/Filament/Resources/DiscountResource/Pages/CreateDiscount.php), [EditDiscount.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/barulagi/app/Filament/Resources/DiscountResource/Pages/EditDiscount.php) |
| [FlashSalePages.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/barulagi/app/Filament/Resources/FlashSaleResource/Pages/FlashSalePages.php) | [ListFlashSales.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/barulagi/app/Filament/Resources/FlashSaleResource/Pages/ListFlashSales.php), [CreateFlashSale.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/barulagi/app/Filament/Resources/FlashSaleResource/Pages/CreateFlashSale.php), [EditFlashSale.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/barulagi/app/Filament/Resources/FlashSaleResource/Pages/EditFlashSale.php) |

> [!WARNING]
> This was a **production bug** — autoloading errors on some deployment environments (e.g. `composer install --optimize-autoloader`). Fixed before deploy.

